### Yearly top 5 species 
```{r}
species_year <- cleanseafood_data |>
  filter(Commodity %in% c("Imports", "Exports")) |>
  group_by(CalendarYear, Commodity, Species) |>
  summarise(Total_tonnes = sum(Volume_tonne, na.rm = TRUE),
